description:
Aislinn Wishart is a third year at Miyamori Girl`s High, plays sergeant position. Originally from New Zealand, she communicates with her teammates with a white board as she doesn`t know the language. There`s nothing flashy nor anything that stands out about her game but according to Kosegawa Shiromi, Aislinn can draw her ideal table like something from a dream. Whenever she plays she always gets a winning hand and in terms of winning percentage she was first in her country.
Source: Wiki
name: Aislinn Wishart
